On a big powerpc box I got the following oops with 2.6.24-git2:
sym0: <1010-66> rev 0x1 at pci 0000:d0:01.0 irq 215
sym0: No NVRAM, ID 7, Fast-80, LVD, parity checking
sym0: SCSI BUS has been reset.
scsi0 : sym-2.2.3
